data.description: Excellent Location. Don't miss this great opportunity, this property speaks for itself. Turn it into the house of your dreams. Four bedrooms and two comfortable bathrooms Spacious, really what you and your families need Located steps from Amelia Park, Schools, Hospitals, Choping Center among others, It is very important for your peace of mind, New Metal Roof with only two months installed,  24/7 recording ,Air Conditioning Chambers of 5 Tons, Heater, Well Water Purifier It has its irrigation system automatically operating daily: Impact Windows. Completely remodeled kitchen You will also love to hear about two Mango bushes, one of Avocado, Lemon, Coconut. Ample Parking for no less than 6 Cars. Make your appointment today!
